License
-------

PyQt5-builder is released under the BSD license.


Installation
------------

PyQt5-builder can be installed from PyPI::

    pip install PyQt5-builder

However you do not normally need to explicitly install it.  It will be
installed automatically when it is needed.


Documentation
-------------

The documentation for the latest release can be found
`here <https://www.riverbankcomputing.com/static/Docs/PyQt5Docs/>`__.
